Date: Wed, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] CVE-2024-28757 false positive documentation for libexpat2 2.2.10-2+deb11u7

---
 ROOT-SECURITY-RELEASE.md | 79 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
